channel.title: How to run a server on a VPS(Virtual Private Server)
channel.description: I recently bought a VPS for my new server. I assumed i wouldn't be portforwarding anything. I logged into my VPS to find out it was already portforwarded but.. My server wouldn't run. If someone can help me with this problem it will be great! Just message me on msn or skype. Both are Maxacollins@gmail.com. Thank you.
